divs: Sighting Details i wnet out my back door to have a cigerette and looked up in the sky and i saw a super bright white light, crossing from nw to se, and it wasn't up high enough to be a satellite, and going too fast ot be a commecerial airliner. don't know what i saw, but i am an avid sky watcher, and never seen something like this. i know i'm not crazy, so if you can check and see if it might have been a satellite for me i would appericate it. i was totaly freaked out, i know i saw something that i usually don't see out here at night
